Package: dfdr
Type: Package
Title: Automatic Differentiation of Simple Functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas", "Mailund", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mailund@birc.au.dk"))
Description: Implementation of automatically computing derivatives
    of functions. Moreover, calculating gradients, hessian and jacobian matrices is possible.
